General.Name: Duketon Mining Ltd
General.Description: Duketon Mining Limited engages in the exploration and evaluation of mineral resources in Australia. The company explores for nickel, copper, platinum, and palladium. Its flagship property is the 100% owned Duketon project located in the Duketon Greenstone Belt, Eastern Yilgarn. The company was incorporated in 2012 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
